OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds
OL,6,Facross the region. Some low cloud is
OL,7,Fpossible in the far east during the
OL,8,Fearly morning, with higher cloud
OL,9,Fcontinuing into southern coasts, clear
OL,10,Fskies with some hazy sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny early cloud clearing to
OL,13,Fgood sunny spells. Still rather hot in
OL,14,Fplaces, especially in the west, but
OL,15,Fperhaps a touch cooler than recent
OL,16,Fdays with the light northerly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
